  "description": "<h3>📢 <strong>Hiring: Radiographer (Private Clinic | 5.5-Day Office Hours)</strong></h3><p><strong>Location:</strong> Orchard<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 🕒 <strong>5.5-day Office Hours</strong></p><p>🩻 </p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform radiographic imaging procedures accurately and safely</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper patient positioning and radiation protection</p></li><li><p>Maintain imaging equipment and ensure compliance with safety standards</p></li><li><p>Assist doctors with imaging requirements as needed</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper documentation and image quality control</p></li></ul><p>✅ </p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Registered with Allied Health Professions Council (AHPC), Singapore</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and professionally</p></li><li><p>Patient-focused with good communication skills</p></li></ul><p>✨ </p><p><strong>Why Join</strong></p><ul><li><p>Stable <strong>office hours (5.5 days)</strong></p></li><li><p>Clinic-based environment</p></li><li><p>Reputable healthcare organisation</p></li><li><p>Good work-life balance</p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Apply Now:</strong><br />📱 <strong>Tele / WhatsApp:</strong> +65 8598 2694<br />Or<br />📧 <strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Michelle@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p><strong>Michelle Ang – Recruit Express Pte Ltd</strong><br />Personnel CEI License No: <strong>R26159565</strong><br />Company License (EA): <strong>99C4599</strong></p>",
